    dc:creator "Gallardo, Fabiana E.; Reche, Vanina Anadina; Bertolaccini, Isabel; Brenda Zarate,; Curis, Cecilia" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A new genus and species of Eucoilinae (Hymenoptera, Cynipoidea, Figitidae) parasitoid of Euxesta eluta Loew (Diptera, Otitidae) attacked Bt sweet corn in Argentina" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.54.10096.figures1-4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.54.10096.figures5-6> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.54.10096.figures1-4>
    dc:description "Figures 1 - 4. Holotype of Euxestophaga argentinensis Gallardo sp. n. Female. 1 Habitus (lateral view) 2 Head and mesosoma (dorsal view), arrow indicates posterior margin of gena distinct, but not carinata 3 Head (posterior view) and mesosoma (dorsal view), arrow indicates basal margin of forewing lacking hair fringe. Male 4 Antenna, arrow indicates posterior margin of scutellum bluntly rounded." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/124108" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.54.10096.figures5-6>
    dc:description "Figures 5 - 6. Holotype of Epicoela seminigra Diaz Female. 5 Antenna 6 Scutellar plate (dorsal view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/124109" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

